Summary.valueString: This document is an invoice from CONTOSO LTD. to MICROSOFT CORPORATION for services rendered during the period from 10/14/2019 to 11/14/2019. The invoice, numbered INV-100 and dated 11/15/2019, details charges for consulting services, document fees, and printing fees, with a subtotal of $100.00, sales tax of $10.00, and a total amount due of $610.00 including a previous unpaid balance of $500.00. The invoice includes billing and shipping addresses in Redmond, WA, and payment instructions to remit to Contoso Billing in New York, NY.
